channel.title: IOS 6 JailBreak Untethered Released
channel.description:
For people out there who have Iphones, Ipods, Ipads and are currently running on IOS 6 through 6.1 then I have news or you!
A Untethered Jailbreak is finally released and I decided to make an alternative download site for the Jailbreak!
The founder of this jailbreak is the evasi0n team which the official site is linked on my site! If you are interested in jailbreaking, download the evasi0n tool!
My Alternative Download Site - [url=http://www.ios6jb.freevar.com]http://www.ios6jb.freevar.com[/url]
The Jailbreak works on all Devices (Iphone 5, 4s, 4) (Ipod 5, 4) All Ipads

item.title: IOS 6 JailBreak Untethered Released
item.dc:creator: @robonick8 robonick8
item.description:
@robonick8 wrote:

[quote=“CoonHunter, post:7, topic:481439”][quote author=robonick8 link=topic=599675.msg4213805#msg4213805 date=1359938323]

There is a developers release from redsn0w that’s been out for weeks, glad to here its almost official.

I dont think it was Untethered… It was probably Semi-Untethered but yea im glad too
[/quote]
It was untethered, was for A4 or earlier devices, and not but around a 70% chance it worked and stayed. That’s why it was a developers release lol. Basically a proof of concept.[/quote]

Never knew that I have A5 so this up coming release benefits everyone 15 and up!

item.title: IOS 6 JailBreak Untethered Released
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“robonick8, post:3, topic:481439”][quote author=the elve age link=topic=599675.msg4213628#msg4213628 date=1359923640]
I might get it, but I don’t want it to void my iPhone 5 warranty
[/quote]

If you crack your screen or whatever just restore it with Itunes and they wont be able to tell if it was Jailbroken!! :D[/quote]
Depending on the jailbreak.

This is why I loved my ipod touch warrenty w/ best buy. It covered accidental breakage.
So when even I jailbroke my ipod and something broke beyond repair, I waterboarded the thing till it stopped working, and brought it back to them.

Or, I just broke it for shits and giggles, because, hey, I could.
